text_blocks.text:
Membership of the Committee consists of:
* His Excellency, the Vice President;
* Hon. Minister, Finance, Budget & National Planning;
* Hon. Minister of State, Budget and National Planning;
* Hon. Minister, Industry Trade & Investment;
* Hon. Minister, Labour and Employment;
* Hon. Minister of State, Petroleum Resources;
* Governor, Central Bank of Nigeria;
* Group Managing Director, NNPC; and
* Permanent Secretary, Cabinet Office -Secretary

Other Ministers Co-opted:
* Hon. Minister of Agriculture & Rural Development;
* Hon. Minister of Humanitarian Affairs, Disaster
* Hon. Minister of Works & Housing;
* Hon. Minister, Aviation;
* Hon. Minister, Communication & Digital Economy;
* Hon. Minister, Education;
* Hon. Minister, Health;
* Hon. Minister, Interior;
* Hon. Minister, Science & Technology; and
* Hon. Minister of Transportation.
